    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A true historical experience!</strong><br><br>Dive into the rich tapestry of Medieval Europe with our historically grounded Micro-Multiplayer Online Game! Unlike typical fantasy realms, our game immerses you in an authentic medieval setting where you'll embark on a journey through the intricacies of life in this era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Point &amp; Click Mechanic: Navigate seamlessly through the world with our intuitive point-and-click interface.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras/6b2ec123cb3c7b57f88bb2f4da90266d.avif?t=1755525785\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras_big/6b2ec123cb3c7b57f88bb2f4da90266d.avif?t=1755525785 width=800 height=418 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Historical Accuracy: Experience a meticulously crafted world that stays true to the historical context of Medieval Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras/928ea3a114e887d70949daecad8adb19.avif?t=1755525785\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras_big/928ea3a114e887d70949daecad8adb19.avif?t=1755525785 width=800 height=418 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Open World Exploration: Roam freely through vast landscapes teeming with adventure and opportunity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras/f7f3ae0ba8763428292e5850d8124e9e.avif?t=1755525785\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras_big/f7f3ae0ba8763428292e5850d8124e9e.avif?t=1755525785 width=800 height=420 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Diverse Skill System: Master various skills including Woodcutting, Fishing, Cooking, Crafting, Melee, Chivalry, Ranged, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras/1f8a91dae0773c98c2a2848dd4820c24.avif?t=1755525785\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras_big/1f8a91dae0773c98c2a2848dd4820c24.avif?t=1755525785 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Micro-Multiplayer Servers: Interact with up to 50 players per server, creating a dynamic and engaging community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Thrilling Challenges: Confront wild animals, traverse dense forests, rise through the ranks as a knight, and vie for glory in epic battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Community Engagement: Assist villagers, earn their respect, and reap the rewards in the form of coins and recognition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras/3eef37fc2fae4f1249bcdfe981515247.avif?t=1755525785\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras_big/3eef37fc2fae4f1249bcdfe981515247.avif?t=1755525785 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Economic Empowerment: Shape the in-game economy by crafting your own equipment, trading goods, and driving commerce.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras/cc4c19d0e77659f66672941d5a26e190.avif?t=1755525785\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras_big/cc4c19d0e77659f66672941d5a26e190.avif?t=1755525785 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Quests Galore: Embark on exciting quests that will test your skills, courage, and wit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras/7048b7ba083302be41977bf01c9d2781.avif?t=1755525785\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192150/extras_big/7048b7ba083302be41977bf01c9d2781.avif?t=1755525785 width=800 height=418 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Expansive Future: Stay tuned for regular updates and new content additions, promising endless adventures on the horizon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the ultimate cross-play journey on Android, PC, and iOS platforms, anytime, anywhere. Whether you're a seasoned adventurer or a newcomer to the medieval realm, join us and carve your own path through history!</p>",
